        <td bgcolor='dimgray' valign='top' width='100%'><font color='white' face='Verdana, Arial, Helvetica' size='2'>Greetings,<BR>I am trying a necromancer for the first time, and I have a question.</P><P>1. When does it seem to go faster for necromancers? What I mean is, when does the leveling start to seem to go faster than the melees. All I have ever played has been melees or shamans, and right now the necro is just really seeming to be slow. Granted, I have always had this type of problem with Casters, probably why I have never stuck with one. So would really like to know when it starts to get better.</P><P>Thanks<BR>Draj</P><P> </font></td>
