        <TD bgcolor='dimgray' valign='top' nowrap><b><font color='white' face='Verdana, Arial, Helvetica' size='2'>buggwin</font></b></td>
        <TD bgcolor='dimgray' valign='top'><font color='white' face='Verdana, Arial, Helvetica' size='2'>At low levels necros will level slower.<BR>At around 12 it picks up.</P><P>At 24 it starts to get really good etc etc..</P><P>Either way, grouping by all rights should be faster with a good puller.</P><P>It when you have 6 people who are sucking up exp and the puller sucks is where the problem is.</P><P>Soloing is extremely tedious for me, and unless you have things to do while soloing it will seem like it will take longer.</P><P>The nice bonus -Log in and begin killing immediately, go afk for as long as you want while feigned and generally play at your own speed.</P><P>However, i encourage you to pursue your melee. And I know thats a negative shot at necros but I know I just love pumping mana at raids etc.</P><P>I love necro's I just don't like the overall perception of us at high levels (mana pump) and I don't like Verant attitude towards us.</P><P>my 2 cents.</P><P></P><P> </font></td>
